Now you can search for memos by keyword. When create a new memo it is temporarily saved. Fixed a bug in expense log memo.

Cell Add reorder function Now Try to add reorder delete a cell by pressing and holding a cell on the To do list Wish list Expense Log Checker Memo! Set the start day of the week You can set the starting day to Monday or Sunday on a memo that provides the days of the week. Improved memo add flow You can select memo by checking thumbnails on the larger screen in the order of recently used. The frequently used memo settings have been removed. iCloud Sync stabilization It stabilizes iCloud synchronization and displays upload download status.
minor bug is fixed.
Apply Christmas app icon Fixed Bug
Fixed an issue where stickers were not visible when adding stickers during the folder creation Fixed an issue where the app did not go directly to the memo when running the app with the widget

Added sorting function inside the folder You can also use sorting fuction with the sort on off function at the top. If you turn off the sorting function you can set the order of the memo as you want. Modify the order when creating a memo in folder When you create memo in folder The memo order was modified to being at the top.

Home Tab changed order by Memo Folder Type You can also set a folder as the app start screen in Settings. Now meet the folder that you decorated with a beautiful cover right at Folder Tab. Added sorting by date Organize memos with dates such as diaries. Added date on all memos The date is also displayed on memo that don t need the date such as todolist and wishlist. Added date hide function As the date is added to all the memos you can hide the date for any memo you want. Increase the number of checkers from 5 to 7 Now you can check on a weekly basis. Jelly TYPE sticker pack added try using Day of the week alphabet jelly stickers. Sticker selection UI improvement Choose a sticker type faster and use the sticker in tap format. Backup function added by email ICloud synchronization is basic! You can transfer the backup data to your personal e mail and load it again. Fixed a icloud synchronization problem. If the problem persists after the update please give me a DM. memong_app
